Darius Jones - Points

Darius Jones scores a career high 10 points (2020)

On December 06, 2020, Darius Jones set his career high in points in a NCAA game. That day he scored 10 points in Judson Eagles's road loss against Valparaiso Beacons, 85-45. He also had 3 rebounds, 2 assists, 2 steals. He shot 3/7 from two, 1/1 from three, shooting at 50.0% from the field. He also shot 1/3 from the free-throw line.
